{"article_id":"TJKMu71q0QePKyq8","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump said Saturday","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"he was alone in the White House with a plan at the ready","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"to reopen the federal government ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"but close White House advisers and staff said","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"they remained in the dark","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"about how he would end the three-week partial shutdown .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"Trump was slated to spend the day","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"speaking by phone to staff and lawmakers ,","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"one White House official said .","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"In the meantime , it remained unclear how long he would let the longest shutdown in the nation ' s history drag on","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"or whether he planned to declare a national emergency in the coming weeks","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"to secure the funding","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"he has demanded for a wall at the southern border ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"according to four advisers and staff reached by .","depth":4},{"id":14,"text":"\" No one knows what he will do ,","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"and the president has not decided yet ,","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"so it keeps everyone guessing , \"","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"said one Republican close to the White House .","depth":4},{"id":18,"text":"\" This could go on another week","depth":4},{"id":19,"text":"and he could declare an emergency ,","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"or this will go on until February . \"","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"The president did not have any public events listed on his schedule for Saturday and Sunday .","depth":4},{"id":22,"text":"With weather forecasters predicting several inches of snow in Washington ,","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"golf","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"- one of Trump ' s favorite past times -","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"seemed out of the question .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"Instead , he spent the morning tweeting about a New York Times report","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"that the FBI had opened an investigation","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"into whether Trump acted on behalf of Russia early in his presidency","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"and insisting","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Democrats return to Washington","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"to fund his long-promised border wall","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"and reopen the government .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"\" I just watched a Fake reporter from the Amazon Washington Post say","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"the White House is ' chaotic ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"there does not seem to be a strategy for this Shutdown .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"There is no plan , ' \"","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"the president tweeted .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"\" The Fakes always like talking Chaos ,","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"there is NONE .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"In fact , there ' s almost nobody in the W.H . but me...","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"and I do have a plan on the shutdown .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"\" Democrats should come back to Washington","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"and work","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"to end the Shutdown ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"while at the same time ending the horrible humanitarian crisis at our Southern Border , \"","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"he wrote .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"\" I am in the White House","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"waiting for you ! \"","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"On Saturday evening , Trump called into Jeanine Pirro 's show on Fox News ,","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"delivering familiar talking points on the shutdown and border security","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"while urging Democrats to make a deal .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"Asked if he was ready to declare a state of emergency ,","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"the president demurred ,","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"citing hope for congressional action .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"Inside the White House , a handful of staff ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"including senior adviser Stephen Miller ,","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"has pushed the idea","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"of using a national emergency","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"to go around Congress","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"and fund a border wall","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"since early in Trump ' s presidency ,","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"said one former senior administration official .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"But top attorney Pat Cipollone and other administration lawyers have been uncertain","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"whether the president had established enough of a legal basis","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"to go that route .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"Some Republican lawmakers and conservatives also have expressed wariness","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"about pushing the boundaries of executive authority to that extent .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"The fear is that such a move would allow future presidents ,","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"including Democrats ,","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"to lean on Trump ' s example","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"and declare national emergencies","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"to fund all sorts of pet policy projects on everything from health care to climate change .","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"And Trump ' s advisers were unsure of the political ramifications","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"of diverting money from disaster relief projects in places like Puerto Rico , one option","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"the administration has explored .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"\" That ' s always been an idea ,","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"as the White House has thought about additional authorities","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"the president can use , \"","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"said the former senior administration official .","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"\" But I don ' t think","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"they should go for that exit ramp .","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"They should see","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"whether they can break up Pelosi ' s conference","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"and see","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"if they can work out something with them . \"","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"Democrats have remained firm","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"that they would not give the president any additional money","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"to build a border wall .","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"Instead , they have tried to embarrass the White House in recent days ,","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"emphasizing the plight of thousands of federal workers","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"who missed their first paycheck Friday .","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"The administration has tried to alleviate some of the shutdown pain","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"by promising to fund food stamps and send out tax refunds","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"even as the agencies","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"that oversee both programs","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"remain closed .","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"On Friday , a senior Office of Management and Budget official told","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"the agency was also working closely with payroll providers","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"to try to get federal workers checks as soon as possible","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"- a move","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"that suggested","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"the administration was starting to feel pressure politically .","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"\" We expect","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"once appropriations are available","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"and time and attendance is submitted ,","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"employees will receive a paycheck for all excepted work as soon as possible","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"( within 2-4 business days ) , \"","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"the official said .","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"\" When legislation is passed for back pay ,","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"furloughed employees would likely receive a paycheck on the same schedule . \"","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":223,"left":132,"right":222,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":125,"right":131,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":120,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":117,"right":119,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":114,"right":116,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":114,"left":0,"right":113,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":113,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":3,"right":115,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":115,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":118,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":123,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":9,"right":122,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":122,"left":10,"right":121,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":128,"right":130,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":127,"right":17,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":126,"right":16,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":130,"left":18,"right":129,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":129,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":222,"left":159,"right":221,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":159,"left":136,"right":158,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":136,"left":21,"right":135,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearit